{"about_the_game":"Deep Sea is a story-driven adventure game where players take on the role of Amara, who is overcome with grief since the death of her grandfather. Amara discovers an imprisoned water spirit that promises to bring her grandfather back, but in doing so is tricked into unleashing a deadly and impassable storm on the islands she calls home.<br><br>Players will have to use the skills learned from Amara\u2019s grandfather to overcome her grief and find a way to weaken and eventually imprison the water spirit. Along the way, they will explore beautiful islands, solve puzzles, and uncover ancient artifacts that hold the key to stopping the storm.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore visually stunning islands, each with their own unique story and challenges to overcome<br></li><li>Discover artifacts lost to time and uncover their hidden past in an attempt to save your home<br></li><li>Listen to an emotionally captivating soundtrack composed by industry veterans<br></li><li>Relive past memories and apply their lessons throughout your journey of self-discovery </li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1499410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1681069943","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1499410/page.bg.jpg?t=1681069943","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1499410/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1681069943","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1499410/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1681069943","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"Deep Sea is a story-driven adventure game where players take on the role of Amar